{
  "video_id": "3752x4PgpYE",
  "title": "Why Vanilla Is So Expensive | So Expensive",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1170.0,
      "end_time": 3989.0,
      "text": "Narrator: You might think of vanilla as basic."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3990.0,
      "end_time": 8990.0,
      "text": "The word is even used to mean boring, average, or basic."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 9200.0,
      "end_time": 11520.0,
      "text": "Student: Why do we have to go all vanilla on this song?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 11520.0,
      "end_time": 13780.0,
      "text": "See what we need is my chocolate thunder."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13780.0,
      "end_time": 17389.0,
      "text": "Narrator: But vanilla may not always be so run of the mill."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19780.0,
      "end_time": 22900.0,
      "text": "Vanilla prices have climbed so high"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 22900.0,
      "end_time": 25300.0,
      "text": "it's worth more by weight than silver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25300.0,
      "end_time": 27830.0,
      "text": "and that high price tag could be bad news"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 27830.0,
      "end_time": 31302.0,
      "text": "for lovers of ice cream, yogurt, chocolate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 31303.0,
      "end_time": 33753.0,
      "text": "and even perfumes."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35410.0,
      "end_time": 38400.0,
      "text": "One reason vanilla has gotten so expensive is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38400.0,
      "end_time": 39800.0,
      "text": "it's hard to grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39800.0,
      "end_time": 43000.0,
      "text": "Vanilla vines take two to four years to fully mature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43000.0,
      "end_time": 47320.0,
      "text": "and their flowers only bloom for one day of the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47320.0,
      "end_time": 49606.0,
      "text": "In order for the plants to produce beans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49606.0,
      "end_time": 52920.0,
      "text": "they have to be pollinated that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52920.0,
      "end_time": 55230.0,
      "text": "In most places where vanilla is grown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55230.0,
      "end_time": 57700.0,
      "text": "it isn't a native plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57700.0,
      "end_time": 59910.0,
      "text": "and there aren't bugs or birds capable"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59910.0,
      "end_time": 61900.0,
      "text": "of pollinating the flowers."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61900.0,
      "end_time": 64489.0,
      "text": "Vanilla is native to Mexico,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64489.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67710.0,
      "text": "but deforestation there has greatly reduced"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67710.0,
      "end_time": 69429.0,
      "text": "its natural habitat."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 69430.0,
      "end_time": 73790.0,
      "text": "In Madagascar, where over 80% of vanilla is produced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73790.0,
      "end_time": 77500.0,
      "text": "the flowers have to be pollinated by hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77500.0,
      "end_time": 80910.0,
      "text": "The pods need several months to cure after harvesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80910.0,
      "end_time": 85700.0,
      "text": "The whole process is time-consuming and labor-intensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85700.0,
      "end_time": 87990.0,
      "text": "But the record high price of vanilla"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87990.0,
      "end_time": 91940.0,
      "text": "also has to do with changes in the vanilla market."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91940.0,
      "end_time": 95000.0,
      "text": "In the 1980s, cheaper artificial vanilla"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95000.0,
      "end_time": 96636.0,
      "text": "overtook the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96636.0,
      "end_time": 99470.0,
      "text": "Vanilla farmers cut back production"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99470.0,
      "end_time": 101920.0,
      "text": "because they weren't making enough money."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 101920.0,
      "end_time": 106920.0,
      "text": "But around 2011, demand for real vanilla rose again."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107600.0,
      "end_time": 110320.0,
      "text": "Big companies were joining the all-natural trend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110320.0,
      "end_time": 113869.0,
      "text": "pledging to eliminate artificial flavorings from their products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 113870.0,
      "end_time": 116910.0,
      "text": "but it's taken a while for the vanilla farmers"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116910.0,
      "end_time": 118619.0,
      "text": "to get back in the game"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 118620.0,
      "end_time": 120563.0,
      "text": "and they don't all want to."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 121900.0,
      "end_time": 125570.0,
      "text": "Growing vanilla is a stressful and volatile business"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 125570.0,
      "end_time": 127850.0,
      "text": "because there is such high demand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 127850.0,
      "end_time": 130470.0,
      "text": "vanilla beans are a target for theft."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130470.0,
      "end_time": 132984.0,
      "text": "After working hard to cultivate their crops"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 132985.0,
      "end_time": 136113.0,
      "text": "some farmers have their beans stolen."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 137400.0,
      "end_time": 140269.0,
      "text": "As the stolen beans move up the supply chain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 140270.0,
      "end_time": 143350.0,
      "text": "they get mixed in with legally purchased beans"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 143350.0,
      "end_time": 145870.0,
      "text": "making it difficult for buyers to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145870.0,
      "end_time": 147740.0,
      "text": "which are which."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 147740.0,
      "end_time": 148800.0,
      "text": "To prevent theft,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 148800.0,
      "end_time": 152340.0,
      "text": "farmers pick the beans before they're ripe"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 152340.0,
      "end_time": 156930.0,
      "text": "and unripe beans means lower quality vanilla."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156960.0,
      "end_time": 159510.0,
      "text": "Farmers also try to prevent theft"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159510.0,
      "end_time": 163160.0,
      "text": "by branding their vanilla crops with a metal pronged brand."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 163160.0,
      "end_time": 168150.0,
      "text": "That way buyers can identify what farm the vanilla came from."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 168150.0,
      "end_time": 173650.0,
      "text": "Farmers also run the risk of having their crops destroyed by extreme weather events."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 173670.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "Cyclones are common in Madagascar"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 179359.0,
      "text": "and climate change is increasing the frequency"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 179360.0,
      "end_time": 182900.0,
      "text": "and intensity of those storms."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 182900.0,
      "end_time": 185540.0,
      "text": "If a cyclone were to wipe out vanilla crops next year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 185540.0,
      "end_time": 189470.0,
      "text": "it would take until at least 2022 for new plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189470.0,
      "end_time": 191320.0,
      "text": "to start producing beans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 191320.0,
      "end_time": 193799.0,
      "text": "and farmers might not want to take that risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193800.0,
      "end_time": 197830.0,
      "text": "So the supply could continue to drop even further."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 197830.0,
      "end_time": 200350.0,
      "text": "The once basic, boring vanilla"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 200350.0,
      "end_time": 205103.0,
      "text": "may wind up becoming a rare sought-after delicacy."
    }
  ]
}